Live Packets
One important thing I learned during provisioning was the importance of keepalive/live packets. I had a recurring issue with my terminal disconnecting from the cloud server during long operations. After research I discovered live packets.They send continuous signals to the server to let it know the SSH terminal is still active, preventing it from dropping the connection.
